message.body: Hello!! How are your classes going? Ready to pull your hair out?

Hey hey hey! Ugh I don't even know where to begin! I haven't felt stress like this in a while. Just trying to keep my head above water. How's nutrition? I saw Gabby the other day! She said she spoke to you recently. It was so unexpected and random! Haven't seen her in so long!

Haha. Well that's so nice! When I go to campus I won't see anyone cause I'll only be able to go at night. But yeah, I thought about her so I figured I'd ask how she was doing. Nutrition is too fast paced for me. I go to bed at like 1, wake up at 5, spend 9 hours with babies, go home, and do it all over again. Haha
Yea, that's rough. These accelerated classes are crazy. The turnover rate is like a day. I'm beginning to lose hope :(
Hahah a day at a time. Are you planning to Di anything for Father's Day?
No. I'm actually going to by studying. Haha. Gooood stuff.
